race.comment: KONSTANTIN (2) spotted a start but wound up strongly late and finished third and beaten 4 lengths (22.13) at Q Lakeside in Maiden. Capable of going well again. MAJESTIC ETHICS (7) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (16.90) at this track behind Chevy Rose in a Maiden. Expecting another good run. SLEEK DESIGN (1) struggling to find form but drawn the rails here. Last time finished 7th in a Maiden on November 10 over 300m at this track behind No Points Left beaten 10 lengths (17.42). Key runner who gets his chance to atone. LITTLE JACK (8) must be among the chances on the last run here.
